Interface Extractor

All Known Implementing Classes:
ExtractorZip
public interface Extractor
Interface for file extractors that define methods for extracting content from compressed files. Implementations of this interface will support different file formats (e.g., ZIP, TAR, etc.) and provide functionality for extracting files and validating supported file types.
